Q1. Separate the following entities into scalars and vectors:
Age, mass, time, length, density, pressure, displacement, velocity, force, specific gravity,
electric current, temperature, momentum, weight and acceleration.
Soln: Scalar entities: Age, mass, time, length, density, pressure, specific gravity, electric current and
temperature.
Vector entities: Displacement, velocity, force, momentum, weight and acceleration.
